# Mixamo Blend Pipeline - Docker Ignore
# Excludes files from Docker build context
#
# Author: Ted Iro
# Organization: Rydlr Cloud Services Ltd (github.com/rydlrcs)
# Date: January 4, 2026
#
# Purpose:
#   - Reduce Docker build context size
#   - Prevent sensitive files from entering container
#   - Speed up build process by excluding unnecessary files

